""" Test close if filename was provided """
filename, fid = hdf_dataset
fof = FidOrFile(fid)
fof.close_if_file_not_fid()
try:
    status = fof.fid.id.valid
except AttributeError:
    status = fof.fid.fid.valid
assert status == 1
